{"tid":249698,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【企鵝認錯】業績「早洩」 騰訊：個別員工人為疏忽","createTime":"2017-05-19T13:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T13:51:22.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf400fafc0161d9891c18a7a58c5f035d9a7ad8","tid":249698,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495192869_c1f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495192869_c1f9.jpg&h=e7d3c6de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n騰訊（700）日前公佈第一季業績，出現「早洩」的情況，事隔三日後騰訊「認錯」。<br />\n<br />\n公司指，一直根據既定的程序發佈業績公告及相關的新聞稿，「在公告正式上載到港交所（388）網站前不慎被上載到騰訊證券的網頁一事，是因為個別員工的人為疏忽，未有嚴格遵守公司既定的程序所致。」<br />\n<br />\n騰訊重申，「雖然有關事件於交易時段完結後發生，但我們仍然非常關注本次事件。在獲悉有關事件後，公司已立即進行調查，並迅速採取一系列改善措施，包括加強現行的程序，以致力確保同類事件不會再次發生。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56716533&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56716533%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=775431fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56716533%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170519&h=68d0f3eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56716533&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170519</a>"},{"pid":"5f864f2e5bde9ee0e3f567258dda054d92310e17","tid":249698,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src